Key Features:
- Real-time policy updates from regulatory changes
- Explainable AI decisions for compliance officers  
- Continuous learning from investigator feedback
- Multi-modal analysis (structured + unstructured data)
- Automated policy versioning and rollback
- Integration with existing AML infrastructure
